      <title>黄金的顺风足以克服“九月魔咒”吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/will-gold-s-tailwinds-be-enough-to-overcome-september-curse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[暑假归来的黄金投资者将急切地想知道这种贵金属是否能够维持创纪录的涨势，还是会遭受九月魔咒的折磨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/will-gold-s-tailwinds-be-enough-to-overcome-september-curse</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
