      <title>亚马逊将聘请 Covariant 创始人来扩展仓库自动化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/amazon-to-hire-covariant-founders-to-expand-warehouse-automation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司正在招聘机器人软件制造商 Covariant 的创始人，此举被称为“收购招聘”，旨在帮助这家电子商务领导者提升其仓库自动化水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/amazon-to-hire-covariant-founders-to-expand-warehouse-automation</guid>
